ChatGPT Clone

A ChatGPT Clone built with Flutter that integrates OpenAI’s GPT API to simulate chatbot conversations. This project demonstrates the seamless integration of AI capabilities into a Flutter-based mobile application with a clean and responsive UI.

📱 Features

	•	Real-Time Chat: Send messages and receive AI-powered responses in real time.
	•	User-Friendly UI: Differentiated user and bot messages for enhanced readability.
	•	Secure API Management: Uses flutter_dotenv to securely handle OpenAI API keys.
	•	Customizable: Modify the UI or chatbot behavior to suit your needs.

🛠️ Technologies Used

	•	Flutter: Frontend framework for building cross-platform apps.
	•	Dart: Programming language used with Flutter.
	•	OpenAI API: For generating chatbot responses.
	•	flutter_dotenv: For secure storage of API keys.

📂 Project Structure

ChatGPT_Clone/
├── lib/
│   ├── main.dart          # Entry point of the application
│   ├── chat_screen.dart   # Chat UI and OpenAI integration
├── .env                   # API key (excluded from Git)
├── pubspec.yaml           # Dependency configuration
├── .gitignore             # Files to ignore in Git
└── README.md              # Project documentation

